<h3 id="-ë²¡í„°ì˜-8ê°€ì§€-ì„±ì§ˆ-">[ ë²¡í„°ì˜ 8ê°€ì§€ ì„±ì§ˆ ]</h3>
<p>-&gt; ë²¡í„°ê³µê°„ì˜ ì„±ì§ˆ</p>

<p>A1 : $\mathbf u + \mathbf v = \mathbf v + \mathbf u$  (â€˜+â€™ êµí™˜ë²•ì¹™)</p>

<p>A2 : $(\mathbf u + \mathbf v) + \mathbf w = \mathbf u + (\mathbf v + \mathbf w)$ (â€˜+â€™ ê²°í•©ë²•ì¹™)</p>

<p>A3 : $\mathbf u + \mathbf 0 = \mathbf 0 + \mathbf u$ ($\mathbf 0$ = â€˜+â€™ í•­ë“±ì›)</p>

<p>A4 : $\mathbf u + (-\mathbf u) = (-\mathbf u) + \mathbf u = \mathbf 0$</p>

<p>S1 : $a(\mathbf u + \mathbf v) = a\mathbf u + b\mathbf v$</p>

<p>S2 : $(a+b)\mathbf u =a\mathbf u + b\mathbf u$</p>

<p>S3 : $a(b\mathbf u) = (ab)\mathbf u$</p>

<p>S4 : $1\mathbf u = \mathbf u 1 = \mathbf u$ (1 = ìŠ¤ì¹¼ë¼ê³±ì— ëŒ€í•œ í•­ë“±ì›)</p>

